EMERGING DISPLAY said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 17.84% to NT$288,098,000 from NT$350,659,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            288,098          350,659    
YOY%             -17.84%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,148,976        1,529,858   
YOY%             -24.90% 
